OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FAll of its attractions use a Ride
OL,8,FAccess Pass (RAP), which is offered to
OL,9,Fguests who find it difficult to stand
OL,10,For cannot do so for long periods of
OL,11,Ftime either due to a physical
OL,12,Fdisability or a learning or emotional
OL,13,Fimpairment.
OL,15,FThe pass allows people access to a
OL,16,F'Virtual Queuing System', where people
OL,17,Fwill wait the queue time outside of
OL,18,Fthe physical line. It does not
OL,19,Fguarantee instant access to the rides,
OL,20,Fbut does decrease queuing time who
OL,21,Fthose who may struggle to line up.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
