OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1770509031
OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FHowever, the London-based operator has
OL,8,Frecently implemented a new RAP system,
OL,9,Fin line Nimbus, its third party
OL,10,Fcompany who assess disability needs
OL,11,Fand provide the 'Access Card'. But,
OL,12,Fsome pass holders have called the move
OL,13,F'discriminatory'.
OL,15,FThe move involves two separate symbols
OL,16,Ffor the pass - 'Difficulty Standing'
OL,17,Fand 'Difficulty with Crowds' -
OL,18,Fcompared to just one which included
OL,19,Fall disabilities - 'Difficulty
OL,20,FStanding & Queueing'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
