OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FJason Rose, who volunteers for the
OL,8,FLondon Autism Group Charity, has one
OL,9,Fof the old ride access passes and has
OL,10,Fused it a number of times taking his
OL,11,Fchildren to theme parks. He is one of
OL,12,Fthousands of people urging Merlin
OL,13,FEntertainments to revert back to the
OL,14,Fold RAP system.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News London James
OL,17,Fsaid: "It is just incredibly
OL,18,Ffrustrating that a whole raft of
OL,19,Fpeople will no longer have access to
OL,20,Fthe parks.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
