PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F408A1770509031
OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,F"This is 21st century and we're trying
OL,8,Fto be inclusive. We've got a better
OL,9,Funderstanding of neurodivergence and
OL,10,Fthis doesn't have a negative impact on
OL,11,Fanyone else.
OL,13,F"People are still waiting just as
OL,14,Flong, they're just not waiting the
OL,15,Fline. And I know there's a perception
OL,16,Fthat people are just turning up and
OL,17,Fgoing straight onto the rides, but
OL,18,Fthey've been waiting somewhere else
OL,19,Ffor just as long as those people in
OL,20,Fthe queue.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
