OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,F"So it's just creating a situation.
OL,8,FWhereas before it was equitable, now
OL,9,Fit is inequitable and it is
OL,10,Fdiscriminatory."
OL,12,FThe change means people with
OL,13,Fdisabilities, including ADHD and
OL,14,Fautism, could be removed from
OL,15,Freceiving a RAP, leaving them joining
OL,16,Fthe psychical queue.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
