OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FThe old RAP system involved one
OL,8,FStanding and Queuing symbol - which
OL,9,Frecognised anyone with a disability
OL,10,Fand gave them access to the pass. It
OL,11,Fmeant those who are neurodivergent,
OL,12,Ffor example, could access the adjusted
OL,13,Fqueueing system.
OL,15,FIn December last year, Nimbus
OL,16,Fannounced its new system would split
OL,17,Fthe RAP criteria into two separate
OL,18,Fsymbols, 'Difficulty Standing' and
OL,19,F'Difficulty with Crowds'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
