OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FThe 'Difficulty Standing' symbol 'is
OL,8,Fallocated to applicants whose mobility
OL,9,Fimpairment makes standing for
OL,10,Fprolonged periods difficult or
OL,11,Fimpossible'.
OL,13,FWhile, the 'Difficulty with Crowds'
OL,14,Fsymbol 'is allocated to applicants who
OL,15,Fhave difficulty being in crowded
OL,16,Fsituations or queues, often due to
OL,17,Fneurodivergence, anxiety, or other non-
OL,18,Fphysical conditions'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
