OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,FNimbus said the change is a direct
OL,8,Fresult of the scheme's growth and
OL,9,Fmeans attractions can now offer more
OL,10,Ftailored support, recognising the need
OL,11,Ffor queue assistance can come from
OL,12,Fvery different requirements.
OL,14,FThe changes were part of a two-year
OL,15,Ftrial by Nimbus and came into effect
OL,16,Fon February 2.
