OL,7,FIn a statement, Rob Smith, Chief
OL,8,FOperating Officer for Merlin
OL,9,FEntertainments, said: "Our guests with
OL,10,Fadditional accessibility needs have
OL,11,Fincreasingly told us that the Ride
OL,12,FAccess Pass simply isn't working for
OL,13,Fthem, particularly as demand has grown
OL,14,Fand queue times for these guests have
OL,15,Fincreased.
OL,17,F"We have listened to this feedback and
OL,18,Fhave been looking at how we can
OL,19,Fimprove the system and find a solution
OL,20,Fthat is in the best interests of all
OL,21,Fguests.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
