OL,3,CLegoland, Thorpe Park and Sealife
OL,4,Cowner under fire after new disability
OL,5,Cpass
OL,7,F"We are also trialling a refined
OL,8,Feligibility criterion during the brief
OL,9,Fopening period of February half term,
OL,10,Fhowever we recognise this has raised
OL,11,Fconcerns for some guests.
OL,13,F"Our commitment to supporting
OL,14,Fneurodiverse guests and those with
OL,15,Fmental health needs remains. We are
OL,16,Flistening carefully to this feedback
OL,17,Fand are committed to keeping this
OL,18,Fapproach under review ahead of our
OL,19,Fmain season openings in March," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
