OL,7,FMr Smith went on to say Merlin
OL,8,FEntertainments "remains deeply
OL,9,Fcommitted to creating inclusive
OL,10,Fexperiences and ensuring all guests
OL,11,Ffeel supported when visiting
OL,12,Fattractions"
OL,14,FHe added: "This is an ongoing journey,
OL,15,Fand we continue to listen, learn and
OL,16,Fadapt by working closely with our
OL,17,Fguests and trusted accessibility
OL,18,Fexperts to better understand
OL,19,Findividual needs and put the right
OL,20,Fsupport in place."
